Transformers, Revenge of the Fallen (2009)

Dutch
De strijd op aarde is voorbij, maar die in het universum is net begonnen.
Wanneer Sam Witwicky (Shia LaBeouf) de waarheid leert over de oude oorsprong
van de Transformers, moet hij zijn lot accepteren en zich samenvoegen met
Optimus Prime en Bumblebee in hun epische strijd tegen de Decepticons, die
sterker terug zijn dan ooit en het plan hebben om onze wereld te vernietigen.

English
A youth chooses manhood. The week Sam Witwicky starts college, the
Decepticons make trouble in Shanghai. A presidential envoy believes it's
because the Autobots are around; he wants them gone. He's wrong: the Decepticons
need access to Sam's mind to see some glyphs imprinted there that will lead them
to a fragile object that, when inserted in an alien machine hidden in Egypt for
centuries, will give them the power to blow out the sun. Sam, his girlfriend
Mikaela Banes, and Sam's parents are in danger. Optimus Prime and Bumblebee are
Sam's principal protectors. If one of them goes down, what becomes of Sam?
